title: Can we help you find your next home? 1x1 ,2x1 and 2x2.  Waiting list
posting_body: Thank you for your interest in Brookhaven Apartments Homes!
1x1, 2x1 and 2x2 Apartment Homes in a great location.
Talking names and number for waiting list.
Get on our waiting list now.
Access to everything you would need.
- Each apartment home is fully equipped with a frost-free refrigerator, multi-cycle dishwasher and electric stove
- Full-sized washer and dryer in every apartment home
-wired for cable television in living rooms and
- Wood burning fireplaces with mantles and tile accents
- Faux granite counter tops in kitchens and baths*
- Reserved car space for each apartment Home
- Qualified pets welcome (weight and breed restriction)
Monthly pet rent $25 per pet per month
For further details, please contact the leasing office
